,(52,7,'_edit_last','1'),(53,7,'h1_title','PSD to HTML Conversion'),(54,7,'_h1_title','field_56225a7d7c7eb'),(55,7,'h2_title','WE TURN YOUR AMAZING DESIGNS INTO BEAUTIFUL CODE.'),(56,7,'_h2_title','field_56225a7d7cfcf'),(57,7,'intro_paragraph','Send us your design and we\'ll return pixel-perfect markup that is tested cross-browser and written in valid WC3 HTML5 / XHTML / CSS markup, with service and turnaround times that can\'t be beat. Code My Views specializes in fast turnaround, high quality HTML markup for our clients. With expert front-end developers and decades of experience in software development, we turn aroundclean, semantic HTML/CSS code fast from your designs.\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>PSD to HTML with Us</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"list\">\r\n	<li><strong>ProfessionallyCoded, pixel-perfect HTML5/CSS3 matchingyour PSD file</strong></li>\r\n	<li><b>Dedicated Project Manager, hands on service.</b></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Standard jQuery and JavaScript covered (menus, sliders, tooltips, light boxes, and more)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"ico ico-103\"><strong>SEO Semantic Code</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Custom fonts included</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Tested and compatible with all modern browsers (IE9+, Firefox, Safari)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>W3C valid code</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Code so good your developerasks for CodeMyViews</strong></li>\r\n</ul>'),(58,7,'_intro_paragraph','field_56225a7d86201'),(59,7,'title_tag','Amazing PSD to HTML.  Pixel Perfect Everytime.'),(60,7,'_title_tag','field_56225a7d86503'),(61,7,'meta_description','Code My Views turns your designs into pixel-perfect HTML / CSS code, fast. Get a quote for your PSD to HTML project in an hour or less!'),(62,7,'_meta_description','field_56225a7d86637'),(63,7,'thumbnail',''),(64,7,'_thumbnail','field_56225a7d86763'),(65,7,'bottom_call_to_action_header','Get a free quote for your PSD to HTML project'),(66,7,'_bottom_call_to_action_header','field_56225a7d8688f'),(67,7,'bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','All of our quotes are good for 365 days, come back whenever you are ready!'),(68,7,'_bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','field_56225a7d869ba'),(69,7,'call_to_action_button_text','I Want a Free Quote'),(70,7,'_call_to_action_button_text','field_56225a7d86b49'),(71,7,'call_to_action_destination','https://codemyviews.com/quote'),(72,7,'_call_to_action_destination','field_56225a7d86cae'),(73,7,'call_to_action_button_bottom_text','We usually reply in less than an hour <i class=\"fa fa-smile-o\"></i>'),(74,7,'_call_to_action_button_bottom_text','field_56225a7d86df2'),(75,7,'tabs_0_tab_text','Overview'),(76,7,'_tabs_0_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(77,7,'tabs_0_icon','fa-info-circle'),(78,7,'_tabs_0_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(79,7,'tabs_0_content','<h4><strong>PSD to HTMLConversion</strong></h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://codemyviews.com/quote\" target=\"_blank\">Upload Your Designs</a></li>\r\n	<li>Receive Free Quote</li>\r\n	<li>SelectDelivery Date</li>\r\n	<li>Payment Confirmation</li>\r\n	<li>HTML / CSS Markup Delivered</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4>How It Works - PSD to HTML</h4>\r\nPSD to HTML is the process of turning your designs into code. Send us any common design file, usually a .PSD, which is the file type used by Adobe Photoshop. Once our team has your designs, we review the files and respond with a quote in an hour or less. Design best practice is to have well-labeled layers with folders and subgroups and include all of your designs for each page in a single PSD file.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/codemyviews-blog-post-images/wp-content/uploads/psd-icon.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-20 alignleft\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/codemyviews-blog-post-images/wp-content/uploads/psd-icon.png\" alt=\"Convert PSD to HTML\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWhen we send you a quote for your project, you\'ll receive a guaranteed delivery date for your markup, along with pricing options for each delivery. You can be assured that we\'ll delivery your PSD to HTML project on time and pixel perfect. After payment is processed you\'ll receive updates to your project via our easy to use client portal. When your markup is ready for review, we\'ll deliver itvia the client portal for your approval. We\'re so confident that you\'ll love the HTML/CSS markup that we offer a 100% money back guarantee.\r\n<h4>What You\'ll Receive</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"list\">\r\n	<li><strong>Hand coded, pixel-perfect HTML5/CSS3 from your Photoshop files</strong></li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"ico ico-102\"></span><strong>Standard jQuery animations - sliders, tooltips &amp; more</strong></li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"ico ico-103\"></span><strong>Semantic code (think SEO)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"ico ico-104\"></span><strong>Custom fonts included</strong></li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"ico ico-105\"></span><strong>Tested and compatible with all modern browsers (IE9+)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"ico ico-106\"></span><strong>Dedicated project manager and personal service</strong></li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"ico ico-107\"></span><strong>W3C validated code</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4></h4>'),(80,7,'_tabs_0_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(81,7,'tabs_1_tab_text','Why Us'),(82,7,'_tabs_1_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(83,7,'tabs_1_icon','fa-question-circle'),(84,7,'_tabs_1_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(85,7,'tabs_1_content','<h4>WebExperts</h4>\r\nWith thousands of projects under our belt, you know that you can trust our team to deliver high quality markup, on-time and ready for production. We\'ve worked with Fortune 500 clients to software startups to deliver PSD to HTML projects serving millions of page views. If you want PSD to HTML done right, trust the Code My Views.com PSD to HTML team.\r\n<h4>Benefits of PSD to HTML Partnership</h4>\r\nUsing Code My Views for your PSD to HTML projects means you have a partner you can rely on. You can optimize your team so that we are your go-to front end developers, or augment your existing team when the project flow is heavy. No matter what, you know that when you partner with us, you have a professional, expert level development team on your side for PSD to HTML projects.'),(86,7,'_tabs_1_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(87,7,'tabs_2_tab_text','How It Works'),(88,7,'_tabs_2_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(89,7,'tabs_2_icon','fa-list-alt'),(90,7,'_tabs_2_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(91,7,'tabs_2_content','<h4>Part 1-Technical Review</h4>\r\nTo start, one of our U.S.-based developers reviews your PSD design files to ensure the design elements for a successful PSD to HTMLand CSS conversion are present. What we are looking for is this:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Designs for each view you want coded</li>\r\n	<li>For JavaScript or jQuery animations; any hover states, dropdowns, tooltips, sliders, lightboxes, modal popups, form validations, and any other interactive or animated elements that you want present in the final HTML markup</li>\r\n	<li>Well named and easy to understand folder and layer names (this is wherewe get our CSS class names)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAfter your Photoshop design files have been reviewed by a developer, we will provide you with a quote.\r\n<h4>Part 2 - Quote</h4>\r\nAfter your PSD designs have been reviewed by a developer you are ready for a quote. Each project is priced on a per page basis, with one PSD file for each HTML file you want to receive. Additional charges include things like JavaScript or jQuery animations.When we provide a quote you will always see:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Guaranteed Delivery date</li>\r\n	<li>Project Brief</li>\r\n	<li>Rush Options Available</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou simply choose a delivery date and enter payment information to kick off development.\r\n<h4>Part 2-ExpertlyCodedMarkup</h4>\r\nAs soon as your project enters the queue, an expert front-end engineer is starting the PSD to HTML process where we hand-code your designs into pixel-perfect HTML / CSS3 code. All of the elements in your design are brought to life; this includes the positioning, colors, images, fonts, line-heights all from the layer properties in the PSD design file. Our team hand codes based off your Photoshop file and turns those elements into pixel perfect HTML code. We review each layer in your Photoshop file and match your designs exactly in our HTML markup.\r\n\r\nAll code is written by expert front-end engineers in HTML5 with external CSS (or SASS, SCSS, LESS) using the latest web standards. After initial development code is validated to make sure there are no HTML validation errors.\r\n<h4>Part 3- Animations &amp; JavaScript</h4>\r\nAfter the initial development of the HTML and CSS markup from your PSD designs, our JavaScript developers can get started on coding any jQuery animations and other JavaScript builds. We have Senior Engineers available for custom JavaScript development and experience working with a variety of JavaScript frameworks. For PSD to HTML, we tend to stick with jQuery for the most common animations to keep code clean and easy for our clients to maintain.\r\n<h4>Part 4 - QAand Delivery of your HTML</h4>\r\nAfter our team finalizes any animations, our Quality Inspectionteam reviews your markup and tests in all the latest browsers, as well as on major mobile and tablet devices.We then will deliver your PSD to HTML project via our white labeled client approval site for end-client approval and sign off.\r\n\r\nWhenever you\'re ready to give PSD to HTML a try, we\'re here! Code My Views is your PSD to HTML partner.'),(92,7,'_tabs_2_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(93,7,'tabs_3_tab_text','Fast Turnaround'),(94,7,'_tabs_3_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(95,7,'tabs_3_icon','fa-rocket'),(96,7,'_tabs_3_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(97,7,'tabs_3_content','<h4>PSD to HTML Code at the Speed of Light</h4>\r\nNeed your PSD to HTML code delivered fast? We\'ll turn around pixel perfect markup in as little as 24 hours for one page. Get started building your rocket ship with ultra-fast delivery PSD to HTML from Code My Views.\r\n\r\nDelivery Times:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fast: 7 business days</li>\r\n	<li>Faster: 3-5 business days</li>\r\n	<li>Fastest: 24-48 hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Guaranteed Delivery</h4>\r\nWith our guaranteed delivery dates, you know you can count on us to deliver on time or we\'ll give you a100% refund.'),(98,7,'_tabs_3_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(99,7,'tabs','7'),(100,7,'_tabs','field_56225a7d8704e'),(101,8,'_edit_lock','1445096640:1'),(102,8,'_edit_last','1'),(103,8,'h1_title','PSD to Bootstrap Development'),(104,8,'_h1_title','field_56225a7d7c7eb'),(105,8,'h2_title','We craft twitter bootstrap like its nobody\'s business.'),(106,8,'_h2_title','field_56225a7d7cfcf'),(107,8,'intro_paragraph','Twitter Bootstrap is an open-source framework that is one of the most popular front-end development frameworks for mobile websites, responsive websites, and apps. With experts in Twitter Bootstrap development on the Code My Views team, we help you to leverage Bootstrap\'s leading mobile features and make sure your website is mobile-first from the start.This site is built on a custom twitter bootstrap theme.\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Fully Responsive</strong></h4>\r\nYour website, application or Bootstraptheme will resize and respond like the beautiful code it is,no matter whichscreen-size you are looking at.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Powerful and Clean</strong></h4>\r\nBootstrap is a framework witha flexible butadvanced code base, so you\'ll always be ready for the next mobile device and future-proof with it\'s clean code structure.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h4></h4>'),(108,8,'_intro_paragraph','field_56225a7d86201'),(109,8,'title_tag','Twitter Bootstrap Yum'),(110,8,'_title_tag','field_56225a7d86503'),(111,8,'meta_description','Code My Views are the expert in Twitter Bootstrap development. Send us your designs and get Bootstrap markup back fast!'),(112,8,'_meta_description','field_56225a7d86637'),(113,8,'thumbnail',''),(114,8,'_thumbnail','field_56225a7d86763'),(115,8,'bottom_call_to_action_header','Get a free quote for your Twitter Bootstrap project'),(116,8,'_bottom_call_to_action_header','field_56225a7d8688f'),(117,8,'bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','All of our quotes are good for 365 days, come back whenever you are ready!'),(118,8,'_bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','field_56225a7d869ba'),(119,8,'call_to_action_button_text','I Want a Free Quote'),(120,8,'_call_to_action_button_text','field_56225a7d86b49'),(121,8,'call_to_action_destination','https://codemyviews.com/quote'),(122,8,'_call_to_action_destination','field_56225a7d86cae'),(123,8,'call_to_action_button_bottom_text','We usually reply in less than an hour <i class=\"fa fa-smile-o\"></i>'),(124,8,'_call_to_action_button_bottom_text','field_56225a7d86df2'),(125,8,'tabs_0_tab_text','Custom Bootstrap Themes'),(126,8,'_tabs_0_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(127,8,'tabs_0_icon','fa-twitter'),(128,8,'_tabs_0_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(129,8,'tabs_0_content','<h4>Your Designs, In Bootstrap</h4>\r\nWe\'ll take your designs and turn them into a custom bootstrap theme for your website. This will create extendable, easy to use solutions to build your web application or website with a consistent and clean design. Bootstrap is a great framework for mobile-first development and we\'ll work with you to build beautiful, clean, responsive Bootstrap code for your site.\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h4>Mobile-First</h4>\r\nOur expert developers make sure yoursite is fully compatiblewith all modern browsers and popular mobile devices using the popular Bootstrap framework.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h4>Feature Rich</h4>\r\nOur front-end engineers and Bootstrap experts will implement all of the features you need to effectively use theextensive Bootstrap components.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column\"></div>'),(130,8,'_tabs_0_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(131,8,'tabs','4'),(132,8,'_tabs','field_56225a7d8704e'),(165,10,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/images.png'),(166,10,'amazonS3_info','a:3:{s:6:\"bucket\";s:28:\"codemyviews-blog-post-images\";s:3:\"key\";s:29:\"wp-content/uploads/images.png\";s:6:\"region\";s:0:\"\";}'),(167,10,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:416;s:6:\"height\";i:102;s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"2015/06/images.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"images-150x102.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:102;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:17:\"images-300x74.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:74;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(168,11,'_edit_lock','1445096666:1'),(169,11,'_edit_last','1'),(170,11,'h1_title','PSD to Email Templates'),(171,11,'_h1_title','field_56225a7d7c7eb'),(172,11,'h2_title','Turn your designs into custom email templates for your marketing campaigns'),(173,11,'_h2_title','field_56225a7d7cfcf'),(174,11,'intro_paragraph','PSD to Email from Code My Views is great for your email templates. Our experts simply code beautiful custom email marketing newsletter templates for your campaign or transactional email. We test cross-device to make sure your newsletter is perfect.We support MS Outlook 2007+, Outlook Express, Apple Mail, Mozilla Thunderbird, AOL Webmail, Yahoo! Mail, Windows Live Mail, Gmail, and Outlook.com.\r\n<h4><strong></strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Get Custom Marketing Campaign Email Templates for your Company from Code My Views.</strong></h4>'),(175,11,'_intro_paragraph','field_56225a7d86201'),(176,11,'title_tag','PSD to Email'),(177,11,'_title_tag','field_56225a7d86503'),(178,11,'meta_description','PSD to Email from Code My Views means you\'ll get pixel perfect email templates for your marketing campaigns, fast!'),(179,11,'_meta_description','field_56225a7d86637'),(180,11,'thumbnail',''),(181,11,'_thumbnail','field_56225a7d86763'),(182,11,'bottom_call_to_action_header','Get a free quote for your PSD to Email project'),(183,11,'_bottom_call_to_action_header','field_56225a7d8688f'),(184,11,'bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','All of our quotes are good for 365 days, come back whenever you are ready!'),(185,11,'_bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','field_56225a7d869ba'),(186,11,'call_to_action_button_text','I Want a Free Quote'),(187,11,'_call_to_action_button_text','field_56225a7d86b49'),(188,11,'call_to_action_destination','https://codemyviews.com/quote'),(189,11,'_call_to_action_destination','field_56225a7d86cae'),(190,11,'call_to_action_button_bottom_text','We usually reply in less than an hour <i class=\"fa fa-smile-o\"></i>'),(191,11,'_call_to_action_button_bottom_text','field_56225a7d86df2'),(192,11,'tabs_0_tab_text','PSD to Email Process'),(193,11,'_tabs_0_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(194,11,'tabs_0_icon','fa-envelope'),(195,11,'_tabs_0_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(196,11,'tabs_0_content','<h4>Email Templates Are Hard</h4>\r\nCommunicating with customers and clients via email is key to the success of your business. Supporting every email client, it turns out, is hard. Code My Views can help make sure your customers get the email message you want to send, a pixel-perfect one, every time. We support the major email clients that your customers use, and test across devices, pixel-perfect like ourPSD to HTML product.\r\n<h4>Beautiful Templates, No Headache</h4>\r\nEmail marketing and keeping top of mind with your customers and clients using email is one of the most important tools for any company. With hundreds of different devices and dozens of different email clients in the browser, plus desktop clients, and now mobile devices - getting emails to look right on every device is increasingly difficult. Trust our experts at Code My Views to have your email template expertly coded.\r\n<h4>PSD to EmailConversion Process</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://codemyviews.com/quote\" target=\"_blank\">Upload Your Designs</a></li>\r\n	<li>Receive Free Quote</li>\r\n	<li>SelectDelivery Date</li>\r\n	<li>Payment Confirmation</li>\r\n	<li>HTML / CSS Email Template Markup Delivered</li>\r\n</ol>'),(197,11,'_tabs_0_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(198,11,'tabs','3'),(199,11,'_tabs','field_56225a7d8704e'),(200,12,'_edit_lock','1445097329:1'),(201,12,'_edit_last','1'),(202,12,'h1_title','WordPress Development'),(203,12,'_h1_title','field_56225a7d7c7eb'),(204,12,'h2_title','Custom WordPress Development, Bespoke WordPress Themes'),(205,12,'_h2_title','field_56225a7d7cfcf'),(206,12,'intro_paragraph','WordPress is an amazing tool and the most widely used CMS in the world with nearly 100 million installations. Our Code My Views WordPress experts have built custom WordPress projects, made to order WordPress themes and WordPress Plugins for clients from small blogs to large-budget enterprise implementations.'),(207,12,'_intro_paragraph','field_56225a7d86201'),(208,12,'title_tag','WordPress Development'),(209,12,'_title_tag','field_56225a7d86503'),(210,12,'meta_description','Code My Views is the go to expert for PSD to WordPress development. Turn your designs into a fully fledged CMS, fast, with pixel perfect designs.'),(211,12,'_meta_description','field_56225a7d86637'),(212,12,'thumbnail',''),(213,12,'_thumbnail','field_56225a7d86763'),(214,12,'bottom_call_to_action_header','Get a free quote for your PSD to WordPress project'),(215,12,'_bottom_call_to_action_header','field_56225a7d8688f'),(216,12,'bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','All of our quotes are good for 365 days, come back whenever you are ready!'),(217,12,'_bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','field_56225