ield_56225a7d86201'),(240,13,'title_tag','Web and Mobile Application Development'),(241,13,'_title_tag','field_56225a7d86503'),(242,13,'meta_description','Launch your MVP with Code My Views in 30 days or less. Code My Views Elite team is ready for your advanced web development needs.'),(243,13,'_meta_description','field_56225a7d86637'),(244,13,'thumbnail',''),(245,13,'_thumbnail','field_56225a7d86763'),(246,13,'bottom_call_to_action_header','Get a free quote for your Web Application project'),(247,13,'_bottom_call_to_action_header','field_56225a7d8688f'),(248,13,'bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','All of our quotes are good for 365 days, come back whenever you are ready!'),(249,13,'_bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','field_56225a7d869ba'),(250,13,'call_to_action_button_text','I Want a Free Quote'),(251,13,'_call_to_action_button_text','field_56225a7d86b49'),(252,13,'call_to_action_destination','https://codemyviews.com/quote'),(253,13,'_call_to_action_destination','field_56225a7d86cae'),(254,13,'call_to_action_button_bottom_text','We usually reply in less than an hour <i class=\"fa fa-smile-o\"></i>'),(255,13,'_call_to_action_button_bottom_text','field_56225a7d86df2'),(256,13,'tabs_0_tab_text','Code My Views Elite'),(257,13,'_tabs_0_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(258,13,'tabs_0_icon','fa-paper-plane-o'),(259,13,'_tabs_0_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(260,13,'tabs_0_content','<h4>Elite Application Development</h4>\r\nOur team of elite web, mobile, and wearable application developers are available when you need more than your typical outsourced team. For our Elite clients we take a hands on approach, giving you access to our best engineers and a dedicated project manger. When we build your web application, you\'ll know we\'ll deliver.\r\n<h4>Experienced and Ready</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strong, talented in-house team (in the US)</li>\r\n	<li>20+ years experience</li>\r\n	<li>Test Driven Development with Structured Framework</li>\r\n	<li>Model-View-Controller (MVC) - Time-tested pattern of development, focused on isolating business logic and program actions from layout and design, allowing for reduction in development time and testing.</li>\r\n	<li>Well documented code and latest web standards</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to use APIs</li>\r\n	<li>Clean, easy to maintain code</li>\r\n	<li>Git version control</li>\r\n	<li>Performance, load, and stress testing</li>\r\n	<li>Major browser compatibility</li>\r\n	<li>User Interface and User Experience Experts</li>\r\n</ul>'),(261,13,'_tabs_0_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(262,13,'tabs','7'),(263,13,'_tabs','field_56225a7d8704e'),(307,20,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/psd-icon.png'),(308,20,'amazonS3_info','a:3:{s:6:\"bucket\";s:28:\"codemyviews-blog-post-images\";s:3:\"key\";s:31:\"wp-content/uploads/psd-icon.png\";s:6:\"region\";s:0:\"\";}'),(309,20,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:256;s:6:\"height\";i:256;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2015/06/psd-icon.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"psd-icon-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(310,20,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Convert PSD to HTML'),(311,8,'tabs_1_tab_text','Bootstrap Features'),(312,8,'_tabs_1_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(313,8,'tabs_1_icon','fa-mobile'),(314,8,'_tabs_1_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(315,8,'tabs_1_content','<h4>Bootstrap Conversion Benefits</h4>\r\nThe best of Bootstrap\'s components at your fingertips:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CSS Preprocessors</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile-first</li>\r\n	<li>Responsiveness</li>\r\n	<li>Common components</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBootstrap makes it east to build mobile-first, responsive websites. The reusable components make it easy to deploy common web and mobile functionality to your site without building it all yourself. Bootstrap uses LESS for preprocessing, making it easy to use variables and create modular CSS code.\r\n<h4>No Mobile Designs?</h4>\r\nNot to worry! Just provide your desktop designs and our professional designers willcreate mobile designs for you that will make sure your site looks great on both tablets and smartphones.'),(316,8,'_tabs_1_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(317,8,'tabs_2_tab_text','Bootstrap Process'),(318,8,'_tabs_2_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(319,8,'tabs_2_icon','fa-list'),(320,8,'_tabs_2_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(321,8,'tabs_2_content','<h4>PSD to Bootstrap Conversion: How it works</h4>\r\nPSD to Bootstrap Conversion with Code My Views is simple:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://codemyviews.com/quote\">Upload Your Designs</a></li>\r\n	<li>We Send Quote</li>\r\n	<li>SelectDelivery Date</li>\r\n	<li>Payment Confirmation</li>\r\n	<li>BootstrapHTML / CSS Markup Delivered</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nNo mobile designs? No problem. We\'ll have our team of professional designers create mobile designs so your site is great on desktop, tablets, and smartphones. We\'ll work with your team on integrating delivery of the front-end files into your development workflow.'),(322,8,'_tabs_2_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(323,8,'tabs_3_tab_text','Why Code My Views?'),(324,8,'_tabs_3_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(325,8,'tabs_3_icon','fa-anchor'),(326,8,'_tabs_3_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(327,8,'tabs_3_content','<h4>Code My Views is Your Bootstrap Conversion Team</h4>\r\nWe\'re Bootstrap mavens. We\'ve completed hundreds of bootstrap projects running in production. It\'s a great framework and one of the reasons we use it on our very own site. We\'re here tohelp you work faster and more efficiently by being your Twitter Bootstrap conversion partner.\r\n<h4>Why is Bootstrap great?</h4>\r\n<strong>It\'s powerful</strong>:A flexible and advanced framework is designedfor the future of the web\r\n\r\n<strong>Mobile first</strong>:Designed \'mobile-first\' means your site will look great on any device\r\n\r\n<strong>Responsive</strong>:Bootstrap\'s fluid framework makes your site resize wonderfully on any screen\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(328,8,'_tabs_3_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(335,7,'tabs_4_tab_text','Fully Responsive'),(336,7,'_tabs_4_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(337,7,'tabs_4_icon','fa-mobile'),(338,7,'_tabs_4_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(339,7,'tabs_4_content','<h4>PSD to Responsive</h4>\r\nNeed a responsive website? Code My Views has you covered. We\'ll covert your PSD to pixel perfect responsive HTML / CSS that looks great on desktop, tablets, and smartphones. To have your website coded responsive, just send both desktop and mobile designs. If you don\'t have mobile designs for responsive, our team of professional designers can create mobile designs so your site looks great on any device.\r\n<h4>Optimized for Mobile</h4>\r\nWith our PSD to Responsive service, you can turn your designs into amazing, mobile friend HTML and CSS code. Our team has worked on many, many responsive projects and know we can amaze you with our PSD to responsive HTML service.'),(340,7,'_tabs_4_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(341,7,'tabs_5_tab_text','Twitter Bootstrap'),(342,7,'_tabs_5_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(343,7,'tabs_5_icon','fa-twitter-square'),(344,7,'_tabs_5_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(345,7,'tabs_5_content','<h4>Bootstrap is Mobile First</h4>\r\nOur expert team of front-end developers loves to code using the Twitter Bootstrap front-end development framework. Learn more about <a href=\"https://codemyviews.com/services/bootstrap/\">PSD to Bootstrap</a> conversion projects. Bootstrap was designed as a mobile-first framework, meaning your project will look great on mobile devices and utilize the latest mobile features for the best on-site experience.\r\n<h4>Bootstrap isOpen Source</h4>\r\nTwitter bootstrap is a framework that makes mobile-first web development easy to do and easy to maintain. Most PSD to Responsive projects can be built using our PSD to Twitter Bootstrap HTML conversion. Bootstrap is actively maintained, and as one of the most widely usedfront-end development frameworks, you know it will be supported for years to come.\r\n<h4>Bootstrap has built in Goodies</h4>\r\nBootstrap also includes build in goodies, like ajavascript framework, making it easy to deploy things like modals or other animations. The Twitter Bootstrap framework also includes class definitions making it easy to deploy mobile first HTML to your site with different class column features for different devices.\r\n<h4></h4>'),(346,7,'_tabs_5_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(347,21,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/Screen-Shot-138.png'),(348,21,'amazonS3_info','a:3:{s:6:\"bucket\";s:28:\"codemyviews-blog-post-images\";s:3:\"key\";s:38:\"wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-138.png\";s:6:\"region\";s:0:\"\";}'),(349,21,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:600;s:6:\"height\";i:270;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2015/06/Screen-Shot-138.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Screen-Shot-138-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Screen-Shot-138-300x135.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:135;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(350,22,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/Screen-Shot-137.png'),(351,22,'amazonS3_info','a:3:{s:6:\"bucket\";s:28:\"codemyviews-blog-post-images\";s:3:\"key\";s:38:\"wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-137.png\";s:6:\"region\";s:0:\"\";}'),(352,22,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:584;s:6:\"height\";i:298;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2015/06/Screen-Shot-137.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Screen-Shot-137-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Screen-Shot-137-300x153.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:153;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(353,23,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/Screen-Shot-136.png'),(354,23,'amazonS3_info','a:3:{s:6:\"bucket\";s:28:\"codemyviews-blog-post-images\";s:3:\"key\";s:38:\"wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-136.png\";s:6:\"region\";s:0:\"\";}'),(355,23,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:620;s:6:\"height\";i:356;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2015/06/Screen-Shot-136.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Screen-Shot-136-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"Screen-Shot-136-300x172.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:172;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(356,22,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Convert PSD to Bootstrap'),(357,11,'tabs_1_tab_text','Supported Clients'),(358,11,'_tabs_1_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(359,11,'tabs_1_icon','fa-at'),(360,11,'_tabs_1_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(361,11,'tabs_1_content','<h4>Major Email Clients Supported</h4>\r\nWe offer support for the majority ofcorporate and consumer email clients so you know your email will look perfect no matter which email client it\'s being viewed in. We support Gmail, MS Outlook 2007+, Outlook Express, Apple Mail, Mozilla Thunderbird, AOL Webmail, Yahoo! Mail, Windows Live Mail, and Outlook.com.\r\n<h4>Robust Testing on Mobile and Desktop</h4>\r\nThe Code My Views team brings the same level of professionalism to PSD to Email templates as we do to all our projects. You can rest assured that your email template is being hand coded by HTML and CSS experts with the right testing suite and tools to make sure it comes out just right.'),(362,11,'_tabs_1_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(363,11,'tabs_2_tab_text','Newsletter Approved'),(364,11,'_tabs_2_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(365,11,'tabs_2_icon','fa-inbox'),(366,11,'_tabs_2_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(367,11,'tabs_2_content','<h4>MailChimp and Campaign Monitor</h4>\r\nOur email templates are MailChimp and Campaign Monitor ready, so you can integrate directly with the newsletter software you\'re using. Email templates can get messy, so make sure you are trusting an expert when it comes to your email templates.With a Code My Views email template you know that your newsletter will be ready to go when it comes time to hit send!\r\n<h4><strong>PSD to EmailConversion</strong></h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://codemyviews.com/quote\" target=\"_blank\">Upload Your Designs</a></li>\r\n	<li>Receive Free Quote</li>\r\n	<li>SelectDelivery Date</li>\r\n	<li>Payment Confirmation</li>\r\n	<li>HTML / CSS Email Template Markup Delivered</li>\r\n</ol>'),(368,11,'_tabs_2_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(369,12,'tabs_1_tab_text','WordPress Plugin Development'),(370,12,'_tabs_1_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(371,12,'tabs_1_icon','fa-plug'),(372,12,'_tabs_1_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(373,12,'tabs_1_content','<h4>Custom Plugins</h4>\r\nA WordPress plugin adds functionality to your basic WordPress installation. There are thousands of free and paid plugins available on the internet, but when an existing solution isn\'t available, our team of php engineers will be able to build an amazing WordPress plugin to fit your needs. Our team of WordPress developers work extensively with custom plugins and can build any php functionality you need.\r\n<h4>Easy to Manage</h4>\r\nAll of the Custom WordPress we develop are easy to manage from the WordPress theme. This makes your WordPress theme easy to distribute and use across your or your client sites.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(374,12,'_tabs_1_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(375,12,'tabs_2_tab_text','Advanced WordPress'),(376,12,'_tabs_2_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(377,12,'tabs_2_icon','fa-cogs'),(378,12,'_tabs_2_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(379,12,'tabs_2_content','We are full stack web developers, not just skinning themes here. We\'ll deploy your WordPress installation to the host of your choice, and make sure it\'s set up to properly stage for the end client, including an easy to use CMS system.\r\n<h4>OptionalFeatures</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"optional_list\">\r\n	<li class=\"optn_icon15\">EnterpriseWordPress Applications</li>\r\n	<li class=\"optn_icon15\">Theme Administration Panel</li>\r\n	<li class=\"optn_icon15\">Customizable Themes</li>\r\n	<li class=\"optn_icon16\">eCommerce Development / Shopping Cart Plugin</li>\r\n	<li class=\"optn_icon17\">Commercial/Custom Plugin Implementations</li>\r\n	<li class=\"optn_icon18\">Multi-Lingual Support</li>\r\n	<li class=\"optn_icon19\">Multi drop down Menu Support</li>\r\n</ul>'),(380,12,'_tabs_2_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(393,24,'h1_title','PSD to Bootstrap Conversion'),(394,24,'_h1_title','field_557d09939bc40'),(395,24,'h2_title','We craft twitter bootstrap like its nobody\'s business.'),(396,24,'_h2_title','field_557d099f9bc41'),(397,24,'intro_paragraph','This site is built on a custom twitter bootstrap theme.Twitter Bootstrap is an open-source framework that is one of the most popular front-end development frameworks for mobile websites, responsive websites, and apps. With experts in Twitter Bootstrap development on the CodeMyViews team, we help you to leverage Bootstrap\'s leading mobile features and make sure your website is mobile-first from the start.'),(398,24,'_intro_paragraph','field_557d09bb02d4f'),(399,24,'title_tag','Twitter Bootstrap Yum'),(400,24,'_title_tag','field_557d09e68cd2f'),(401,24,'meta_description','CodeMyViews are the expert in Twitter Bootstrap development. Send us your designs and get Bootstrap markup back fast!'),(402,24,'_meta_description','field_557d0a0497e8f'),(403,24,'thumbnail',''),(404,24,'_thumbnail','field_557d0a2300c10'),(405,24,'bottom_call_to_action_header','Get a free quote for your Twitter Bootstrap project'),(406,24,'_bottom_call_to_action_header','field_557d0a65c9374'),(407,24,'bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','All of our quotes are good for 365 days, come back whenever you are ready!'),(408,24,'_bottom_call_to_action_secondary_text','field_557d0a8a3a9d7'),(409,24,'call_to_action_button_text','I Want a Free Quote'),(410,24,'_call_to_action_button_text','field_557d0ab31b309'),(411,24,'call_to_action_destination','https://codemyviews.com/quote'),(412,24,'_call_to_action_destination','field_557d0ad5eb7b1'),(413,24,'call_to_action_button_bottom_text','We usually reply in less than an hour <i class=\"fa fa-smile-o\"></i>'),(414,24,'_call_to_action_button_bottom_text','field_557d0af8211d6'),(415,24,'tabs_0_tab_text','Custom Bootstrap Themes'),(416,24,'_tabs_0_tab_text','field_557d0b5649cfc'),(417,24,'tabs_0_icon','fa-twitter'),(418,24,'_tabs_0_icon','field_557d0b6849cfd'),(419,24,'tabs_0_content','We\'ll take your designs and turn them into a custom bootstrap theme for your website. This will create extendable, easy to use solutions to build your web application or website with a consistent and clean design. Bootstrap is a great framework for mobile-first development and we\'ll work with you to build beautiful, clean, responsive Bootstrap code for your site.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/codemyviews-blog-post-images/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-138.png\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-21 aligncenter\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/codemyviews-blog-post-images/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-138-300x135.png\" alt=\"PSD to Bootstrap Conversion\" width=\"300\" height=\"135\" /></a>'),(420,24,'_tabs_0_content','field_557d0bd476980'),(421,24,'tabs_1_tab_text','Bootstrap Features'),(422,24,'_tabs_1_tab_text','field_557d0b5649cfc'),(423,24,'tabs_1_icon','fa-mobile'),(424,24,'_tabs_1_icon','field_557d0b6849cfd'),(425,24,'tabs_1_content','<a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/codemyviews-blog-post-images/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-137.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-22 size-medium alignright\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/codemyviews-blog-post-images/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-137-300x153.png\" alt=\"Convert PSD to Bootstrap\" width=\"300\" height=\"153\" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CSS Preprocessors</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile-first</li>\r\n	<li>Responsiveness</li>\r\n	<li>Common components</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBootstrap makes it east to build mobile-first, responsive websites. The reusable components make it easy to deploy common web and mobile functionality to your site without building it all yourself. Bootstrap uses LESS for preprocessing, making it easy to use variables and create modular CSS code.'),(426,24,'_tabs_1_content','field_557d0bd476980'),(427,24,'tabs_2_tab_text','Bootstrap Process'),(428,24,'_tabs_2_tab_text','field_557d0b5649cfc'),(429,24,'tabs_2_icon','fa-list'),(430,24,'_tabs_2_icon','field_557d0b6849cfd'),(431,24,'tabs_2_content','PSD to Bootstrapwith CodeMyViews is simple:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Upload Your Desktop/Mobile Designs</li>\r\n	<li>We Send Quote</li>\r\n	<li>SelectDelivery Date</li>\r\n	<li>Payment Confirmation</li>\r\n	<li>BootstrapHTML / CSS Markup Delivered</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nNo mobile designs? No problem. We\'ll have our team of professional designers create mobile designs so your site is great on desktop, tablets, and smartphones. We\'ll work with your team on integrating delivery of the front-end files into your development workflow.'),(432,24,'_tabs_2_content','field_557d0bd476980'),(433,24,'tabs_3_tab_text','No mobile designs?'),(434,24,'_tabs_3_tab_text','field_557d0b5649cfc'),(435,24,'tabs_3_icon','fa-paint-brush'),(436,24,'_tabs_3_icon','field_557d0b6849cfd'),(437,24,'tabs_3_content','Not to worry! Just provide your desktop designs and our professional designers willcreate mobile designs for you that will make sure your site looks great on both tablets and smartphones.'),(438,24,'_tabs_3_content','field_557d0bd476980'),(439,24,'tabs_4_tab_text','Why Us?'),(440,24,'_tabs_4_tab_text','field_557d0b5649cfc'),(441,24,'tabs_4_icon','fa-anchor'),(442,24,'_tabs_4_icon','field_557d0b6849cfd'),(443,24,'tabs_4_content','We\'re Bootstrap mavens. We\'ve completed hundreds of bootstrap projects running in production. It\'s a great framework and one of the reasons we use it on our very own site. We\'re here tohelp you work faster and more efficiently by being your Twitter Bootstrap conversion partner.\r\n\r\nWhy is Bootstrap great?\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>It\'s powerful\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A flexible and advanced framework is designedfor the future of the web</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile first\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Designed \'mobile-first\' means your site will look great on any device</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Responsive\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bootstrap\'s fluid framework makes your site resize wonderfully on any screen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;'),(444,24,'_tabs_4_content','field_557d0bd476980'),(445,24,'tabs','5'),(446,24,'_tabs','field_557d0b2b49cfb'),(447,25,'_wp_attached_file','https://s3.amazonaws.com/codemyviews-blog-post-images/wp-content/uploads/supported-email-clients-e1435255036978.png'),(449,25,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:30;s:6:\"height\";i:212;s:4:\"file\";s:115:\"https://s3.amazonaws.c