1373,13,'images_1_image','45608'),(1374,13,'_images_1_image','field_56225a7d98ac0'),(1375,13,'images_2_image','45609'),(1376,13,'_images_2_image','field_56225a7d98ac0'),(1377,13,'images','3'),(1378,13,'_images','field_56225a7d86f23'),(1379,13,'tabs_1_tab_text','Programming Guidelines'),(1380,13,'_tabs_1_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(1381,13,'tabs_1_icon','fa-code'),(1382,13,'_tabs_1_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(1383,13,'tabs_1_content','Our team has built and worked on so many web projects, we know what works and what doesn\'t. When you work with an experienced team like Code My Views you know your project will be delivered on time and on point.\r\n<h4>Benefits of Code My Views Application Development</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Create clean applications with APIs that are easy to maintain and hand-off to an end client</li>\r\n	<li>Utilize the most effective project and version management tools</li>\r\n	<li>Foster an environment that makes it easy for multiple programmers to work on the same project</li>\r\n	<li>Deliver well commented and easy to read source code</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure that other developers are easily to understand and familiarize themselves with our code</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1384,13,'_tabs_1_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(1385,13,'tabs_2_tab_text','Your Vision, Our Team'),(1386,13,'_tabs_2_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(1387,13,'tabs_2_icon','fa-rocket'),(1388,13,'_tabs_2_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(1389,13,'tabs_2_content','<h4>Partner With Us</h4>\r\nComplexity delivered in a simple solution  creating powerful web applications capable of heavy lifting.Code My Views delivers your complex application with simple solutions and strong communication. We create powerful applications capable of heavy lifting and scale.Code My Views uses structured programming, test driven development, best programming practices, coding guidelines, and web standards.We are constantly improving ourselves and our skill set for the best possible development solutions for our clients.\r\n<h4>MVC &amp; Test Driven Development</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Programming and business logic is isolated from the User Interface Views (HTML, CSS), making it easy for the Design</li>\r\n	<li>Team or any Designer to edit the interface and make design changes without help from back-end engineers.</li>\r\n	<li>Web application programming builds are based on the module, libraries, and tools most developers use so that any</li>\r\n	<li>programmer can easily share libraries and implement complex functionality in an efficient manner.</li>\r\n	<li>Our structure makes it easy to practice best practice coding with high quality programming standards.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1390,13,'_tabs_2_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(1391,13,'tabs_3_tab_text','Application Frameworks'),(1392,13,'_tabs_3_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(1393,13,'tabs_3_icon','fa-code-fork'),(1394,13,'_tabs_3_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(1395,13,'tabs_3_content','Code My Views has completed thousands of projects with wide ranging web and mobile application development frameworks. We will help you select the best framework for the context of your project ensuring that it is easy to maintain and handoff after initial development. You won\'t be left with a mess that no one knows how to update.\r\n<h4>Web Application Frameworks:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Laravel PHP Framework</li>\r\n	<li>Phalcon PHP Framework</li>\r\n	<li>Symfony PHP Framework</li>\r\n	<li>Ruby on Rails Ruby Framework</li>\r\n	<li>Django Python Framework</li>\r\n	<li>CodeIgniter PHP Framework</li>\r\n	<li>JavaScript Libraries and Frameworks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Mobile Application Development</h4>\r\nWe are experts in Mobile Application development, whether you need a native iOS application written in Swift / Objective-C, an Android application, or a Hybrid mobile application for both iOS and Android platforms, we have experience building them all. Our Mobile Application team has built best selling, #1 ranked iOS and Android applications and is ready for your enterprise grade application.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(1396,13,'_tabs_3_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(1397,13,'tabs_4_tab_text','JavaScript Engineers'),(1398,13,'_tabs_4_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(1399,13,'tabs_4_icon','fa-file-code-o'),(1400,13,'_tabs_4_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(1401,13,'tabs_4_content','Our Team is experienced with the following JavaScript Libraries and Frameworks, and works with its clients to select the JavaScript Libraries and Frameworks that are well suited to each client\'s needs:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>jQuery</li>\r\n	<li>Dojo Toolkit</li>\r\n	<li>Vue.js</li>\r\n	<li>Ext JS</li>\r\n	<li>Backbone.js</li>\r\n	<li>AngularJS</li>\r\n	<li>Google Web Toolkit</li>\r\n	<li>Google Closure Library</li>\r\n	<li>Socket.IO</li>\r\n	<li>Underscore.js</li>\r\n	<li>D3.js</li>\r\n	<li>Node.js</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1402,13,'_tabs_4_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(1403,13,'tabs_5_tab_text','Programming Languages'),(1404,13,'_tabs_5_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(1405,13,'tabs_5_icon','fa-language'),(1406,13,'_tabs_5_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(1407,13,'tabs_5_content','<h4>Application Languages</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PHP</li>\r\n	<li>JavaScript</li>\r\n	<li>Ruby</li>\r\n	<li>Python</li>\r\n	<li>Java</li>\r\n	<li>Objective-C</li>\r\n	<li>Swift</li>\r\n	<li>C#</li>\r\n	<li>C</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4></h4>'),(1408,13,'_tabs_5_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(1409,13,'tabs_6_tab_text','Use Cases'),(1410,13,'_tabs_6_tab_text','field_56225a7d9f5ef'),(1411,13,'tabs_6_icon','fa-desktop'),(1412,13,'_tabs_6_icon','field_56225a7da1971'),(1413,13,'tabs_6_content','One of Code My Views greatest strengths is versatility and scope of services. We areexperienced in all cutting-edge web application technologies. You can\'t beat our team of experienced engineers for your application development project.\r\n<h4>Application Development Use Cases</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Content Management Systems</li>\r\n	<li>eCommerce Development</li>\r\n	<li>Social Networking Development</li>\r\n	<li>Online Reservations Booking and Ticketing</li>\r\n	<li>Educational Web Applications</li>\r\n	<li>Project ManagementSoftware</li>\r\n	<li>Online Training and Professional Development Courses</li>\r\n	<li>Inventory Management Applications</li>\r\n	<li>Online Forums</li>\r\n	<li>Blogs and Self-managed Content Management Systems</li>\r\n	<li>Web Conference Applications</li>\r\n	<li>Non-profit Applications</li>\r\n	<li>HR Web Applications</li>\r\n	<li>Financial Applications and Tools</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1414,13,'_tabs_6_content','field_56225a7da1b0b'),(1415,45648,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/Wordpress-start-image.jpg'),(1416,45648,'amazonS3_info','a:3:{s:6:\"bucket\";s:28:\"codemyviews-blog-post-images\";s:3:\"key\";s:44:\"wp-content/uploads/Wordpress-start-image.jpg\";s:6:\"region\";s:0:\"\";}'),(1417,45648,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:500;s:6:\"height\";i:357;s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"2015/06/Wordpress-start-image.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"Wordpress-start-image-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"Wordpress-start-image-300x214.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:214;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:19:\"facebook_image_size\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"Wordpress-start-image-470x246.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:470;s:6:\"height\";i:246;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"square\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"Wordpress-start-image-500x357.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:500;s:6:\"height\";i:357;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(1418,12,'images_0_image','45606'),(1419,12,'_images_0_image','field_56225a7d98ac0'),(